{"tid":825692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家警察有份鋸樹係係咪一定要吹奏返？","createTime":"2018-09-17T17:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T00:24:26.000Z","uid":39777,"like":17,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3faa697c5deaccab377aad838ad9a9700796b3a4","tid":825692,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"唔只要吹奏，仲要幫黑警抱打不平週圍問點解唔吹奏佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c9293d1fb0c45b224f72e9c35c9e6ac4de3868","tid":825692,"uid":58307,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"義工呀？有人工架！淨係行行企企呀？吹佢老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把市民落街幫手清理，無人工喎仲要。"},{"pid":"85ed5b90c0a83d11e86c76fafc3ad7369cac2eb8","tid":825692,"uid":140769,"like":12,"dislike":11,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:06:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69ea83e672086363800cfef8c190dcc9430bfc11","tid":825692,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"每日一篇，世界更美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d80f1546e3cbf88a0343451de34f7abf832eb3","tid":825692,"uid":17510,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"收啦五毛<br />\n警犬收咁高人工日日行行企企<br />\n<br />\n而家咩做返啲嘢  應該架"},{"pid":"2d5a9fa2ed814ca5851107e3871f9b8fa56e134d","tid":825692,"uid":140769,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T18:21:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10dac9c8f08d766bc27b5f513e769cf71bd13a6e","tid":825692,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T23:57:07.000Z","msg":"見到啲垃圾攞黎同一般市民比<br />\n話尋日返工都係應份<br />\n屌你老母你份工有危險性day1都知架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但普通市民份工唔撚係丫嘛<br />\n想攞黎比你咪唔撈做返個文員仔囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416d014d182c7d4691b5e51eb83c555cee537eb5","tid":825692,"uid":34410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:10:37.000Z","msg":"係得某幾隻連登護警撚撐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da4390db09bd1a83c40167827aa93776a55e543","tid":825692,"uid":65649,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:13:33.000Z","msg":"吹佢老母， 我理閪佢有資源冇資源， on9到哂時間用把指甲挫鋸樹就係哂時間<br />\n<br />\n佢冇工具，個人本身係可以做其他更有幫助既野如搬運清場等，你擺明返工呃鍾扮做野<br />\n<br />\n咪撚以為大家唔知啦死差佬"},{"pid":"ba343e7b94ff5df9249a4e964e4815bacb3d4c9a","tid":825692,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa5453570d198208284b11dcbdf2a754959447f","tid":825692,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"是其是, 非其非<br />\n一單還一單"},{"pid":"8ee14f857e4366a89d0f5c5e902ff242f2cae4d8","tid":825692,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:32:43.000Z","msg":"吹條撚<br />\n淨係周不時砌義士生豬肉同大棍大棍扑柒人呢兩筆債都有排佢哋還"},{"pid":"aa8feee513eafda6227a62e1eb630f5060d26dee","tid":825692,"uid":181703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/103310_1b8c6841e888a310589181c5dd4bd2e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F103310_1b8c6841e888a310589181c5dd4bd2e2.jpg&h=ff2a406d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢把先係木鋸。"},{"pid":"507698fd6bb95dd60b839db3c8d1fd9b2bfa3825","tid":825692,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"They are well paid for it."},{"pid":"f14cc9b5358358576771bb944c63453f69e7ba3d","tid":825692,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:35:19.000Z","msg":"有事就出嚟鏡頭面前做下樣R credit<br />\n<br />\n但係平時啲職責呢? <br />\n畀蝻搞又好,畀人偷電話又好<br />\n明明已經一街天眼,但係就開file都懶得就懶<br />\n<br />\n結論: 警察根本就係well paid得嚟都做唔足本份"},{"pid":"7eaec2f95f7ad19447b4ea53285437eec9615b91","tid":825692,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"442083f285fe2a3b4b6ecbbc2ab9dcb7da8d52ac","tid":825692,"uid":87511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"有心吹奏差佬嗰啲都唔知係五毛定溫室小花<br />\n<br />\n一年打得幾多次風? 係咪次次打風都要佢哋鋸樹? 佢哋又鋸得幾多? <br />\n但係平時成日hea鳩耍走啲報案人呢條數又點計呢?<br />\n<br />\n天眼同香港警察都一樣,唔係保障普通市民生命財產,只係用嚟幫港共為虎作倀嘅工具<br />\n<br />\n有咩值得吹奏? 要吹嗰班連登仔唔該返屋企幫你老豆吹仲好"},{"pid":"2d7caecf2cbe3851c7a2c3fcca0078181bc757fd","tid":825692,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"592ca0577fe1bc497994e1848f745f07822ceb60","tid":825692,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eaec2f95f7ad19447b4ea53285437eec9615b91","tid":825692,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f14cc9b5358358576771bb944c63453f69e7ba3d","tid":825692,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:35:19.000Z","msg":"有事就出嚟鏡頭面前做下樣R credit<br />\n<br />\n但係平時啲職責呢? <br />\n畀蝻搞又好,畀人偷電話又好<br />\n明明已經一街天眼,但係就開file都懶得就懶<br />\n<br />\n結論: 警察根本就係well paid得嚟都做唔足本份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"嘥鳩氣,首先根據我個人經驗,佢哋根本懶得就懶,傷人甚至畀人打劫都唔一定開file幫你查<br />\n肯開最多都只係因為要追quota<br />\n<br />\n另外平時深水埗同元朗每晚鳩叫甚至開片嗰班蝻呢?<br />\n差佬嘅本份係咪應該逗佢哋多啲啊? 本份嚟架喎<br />\n<br />\n本份都做唔好,點吹?"},{"pid":"4daef3831ab05451216c4ce8dcfdaf4832605e90","tid":825692,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7caecf2cbe3851c7a2c3fcca0078181bc757fd","tid":825692,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"442083f285fe2a3